# Memory Index

Generated YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM by `memory_index_generate.py`.
Regenerable — do not hand-edit. Fix sources or tune script instead.

**Sources:** N rules + M decisions.

Flat lists for now — auto-clustering re-introduced when entry count justifies it (~50+).

## Rules (N)

- Rule title pulled from the first `# Heading` of each rule file → [filename.md](memory/rules/filename.md)
- ...

## Decisions (newest first) (M)

- Decision text without the date suffix *(YYYY-MM-DD)* → [working-memory.md](memory/working-memory.md)
- ...
